Here are the current steps to take to build percolator:

1) Build Xerces
$ cd ../xerces
$ ./configure --disable-network
$ make
$ cd ../percolator

2) Load xsd module
$ module load xsd

3) Find where the xsd module is located
$ which xsd

4) Update cmake/FindXSD.cmake with path to binary and include files, ex.

XSD_INCLUDE_DIR
/net/gs/vol3/software/modules-sw/xsd/3.3.0/Linux/RHEL5/x86_64/libxsd
XSD_EXECUTABLE
/net/gs/vol3/software/modules-sw/xsd/3.3.0/Linux/RHEL5/x86_64/bin/


5) Load Boost module
$ module load boost

6) Find where the boost module is loaded
$ echo $LD_LIBRARY_PATH

7) Edit percolator/src/CMakeLists.txt to update CMAKE_INCLUDE_PATHs with directory to boost directory before find_package(Boost ...), ex.

   SET(CMAKE_INCLUDE_PATH "/net/gs/vol3/software/modules-sw/boost/1.45.0/Linux/RHEL5/x86_64/include" ${CMAKE_INCLUDE_PATH})
   SET(CMAKE_LIBRARY_PATH "/net/gs/vol3/software/modules-sw/boost/1.45.0/Linux/RHEL5/x86_64/lib" ${CMAKE_LIBRARY_PATH})
   find_package(Boost COMPONENTS filesystem system REQUIRED)

8) Run cmake
$ module load cmake
$ cmake .

9) run make
$ make

10) YAY!
   

